      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 241,
      "versionNonce": 1714576585,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "3) API Surface (actor-aware; control vs data plane)\n Control Plane (authoritative, async): tenant & quota spec • training/job orchestration • model registry • \n    rollout/approval • usage/budget • audit/break-glass\n Data Plane (serve + observe only): infer • admission result • health/readiness • metrics/logs • \n    telemetry emission\n Access model: write via control plane only; data plane is read/execute-only\n Lifecycle: define → approve → deploy → observe → rollback",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) API Surface (actor-aware; control vs data plane)\n Control Plane (authoritative, async): tenant & quota spec • training/job orchestration • model registry • \n    rollout/approval • usage/budget • audit/break-glass\n Data Plane (serve + observe only): infer • admission result • health/readiness • metrics/logs • \n    telemetry emission\n Access model: write via control plane only; data plane is read/execute-only\n Lifecycle: define → approve → deploy → observe → rollback",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
