    {
      "id": "tx4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 31.646900311373315,
      "y": 1002.4312093291567,
      "width": 792.0694580078125,
      "height": 158.44769466743583,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 509,
      "versionNonce": 339115657,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "4) Data Model ( durability notation for the 4–6 load-bearing data sets )\nControl Plane (authoritative): \n    desired state + policy/entitlements + rollout/workflow state + immutable audit/history\nData Plane: \n    serving/execution: handles requests/jobs; reads desired state; emits telemetry; never the source of truth\n    state: ephemeral runtime only (sessions, leases, caches, checkpoints, rebuildable indices)\nCorrectness rule: writes that change meaning/permissions go through control plane; data plane enforces + reports\nKeys & safety: \n    partition by tenant/resource type/region; idempotency on non-repeatable state transitions",
      "fontSize": 14.084239525994294,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4) Data Model ( durability notation for the 4–6 load-bearing data sets )\nControl Plane (authoritative): \n    desired state + policy/entitlements + rollout/workflow state + immutable audit/history\nData Plane: \n    serving/execution: handles requests/jobs; reads desired state; emits telemetry; never the source of truth\n    state: ephemeral runtime only (sessions, leases, caches, checkpoints, rebuildable indices)\nCorrectness rule: writes that change meaning/permissions go through control plane; data plane enforces + reports\nKeys & safety: \n    partition by tenant/resource type/region; idempotency on non-repeatable state transitions",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a8",
