    {
      "id": "tx5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 42.074564512256586,
      "y": 1186.6207944259043,
      "width": 1090.375,
      "height": 70.00526497037471,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 251,
      "versionNonce": 1768763465,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "text": "5) High-Level Components & Flows\nComponents by responsibility: interface/entry • control/decision • execution/serving • state/durability • async delivery (optional) • observability • external deps.\nCore flows: execution path • change path (propose→approve→persist) • apply/reconcile path • observe path • recover path.\nFlow annotations: auth boundaries • admission/limits • failure behavior (blast radius, fail-open/closed) • visibility/status.",
      "fontSize": 14.001052994074941,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 14,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5) High-Level Components & Flows\nComponents by responsibility: interface/entry • control/decision • execution/serving • state/durability • async delivery (optional) • observability • external deps.\nCore flows: execution path • change path (propose→approve→persist) • apply/reconcile path • observe path • recover path.\nFlow annotations: auth boundaries • admission/limits • failure behavior (blast radius, fail-open/closed) • visibility/status.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aA",
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768513439190,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "sr2",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 26.99218223502953,
      "y": 428.83775871643223,
      "width": 943.576004943849,
      "height": 404.5811526528039,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
